leted with any technical means. The company will take all necessary measures and will notify the applicant about it by e-mail indicated in the claim. If a claim is not accepted for satisfaction or the remedy is not feasible, the company shall provide the applicant with the grounds for its refusal in writing by mail to the address indicated in the claim.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicmedicondosc\">Any claims made by anonyms or delivered by e-mail or fax WILL NOT be accepted and considered.</span></p>','section/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/89/promo_text_03.png',NULL),(90,80,'/web/container','container','/cloud/vps',NULL,NULL,'no','yes','yes','yes',NULL,'Container VPS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(91,50,'/dedicated/vds','vds','/cloud/vds',NULL,NULL,'no','yes','yes','yes',20,'VDS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(92,12,'/admin/site/contentlittle','contentlittle',NULL,'Zero_Main','Content_ContentLittle_Grid','yes','yes','yes','yes',50,'Текстовые вставки','Текстовые вставки','Текстовые вставки','Текстовые вставки',NULL,NULL,NULL),(93,92,'/admin/site/contentlittle/edit','edit',NULL,'Zero_Main','Content_ContentLittle_Edit','yes','yes','no','yes',10,'Текстовые вставки изменение','Текстовые вставки изменение','Текстовые вставки изменение','Текстовые вставки изменение',NULL,NULL,NULL),(94,12,'/admin/site/faq','faq',NULL,'Zero_Main','Content_Faq_Grid','yes','yes','yes','yes',60,'Faq','Faq','Faq','Faq',NULL,NULL,NULL),(95,94,'/admin/site/faq/edit','edit',NULL,'Zero_Main','Content_Faq_Edit','yes','yes','no','yes',10,'Faq Изменение','Faq Изменение','Faq Изменение','Faq Изменение',NULL,NULL,NULL),(96,76,'/about/network','network',NULL,'Content_Page','Content_Section_Page','no','yes','yes','yes',30,'Network','Network','Network','Network','<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">HOSTKEY&rsquo;s network is connected to the largest carriers and traffic exchange points, which guarantees the availability of resources.</span></span></strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF692d;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicmedicondosc\"><span style=\"font-size:26px\"><strong>Russia</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">HOSTKEY&nbsp;is connected to networks of such telecom operators as RETN, NETBYNET, etc. that have direct channels to CITY SYSTEMS, DATALINE and DATAPRO data centers. Networks of these operators are based on highly reliable telecommunication equipment and have multiple redundancy that provides network accessibility of server equipment.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Connection to the network of the international operator RETN makes it possible to provide services with high level of accessibility not only in the Russian Federation:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"color: rgb(255, 105, 45);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">The network uses Internet Exchange nodes in Europe, USA and Asia, and it is constantly growing.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color: rgb(255, 105, 45);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">It is capable of maintaining 100G channels, with a total of 7.2Tbit/s per fiber pair.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF692d;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicmedicondosc\"><span style=\"font-size:26px\"><strong>The Netherlands</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">HOSTKEY has a reserved connection to Serverius network and several traffic exchange points, in particular AMS-IX:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Serverius network provides a mix of huge amount of peering and ip-transit providers: AMS-IX, DE-CIX, Gtt Tiner, Level3, DE-CIX, TATA communications, NL-IX, RETN and many other partial and full transit and private fiber peers.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Each peering or carrier is connected to multiple 10G ports and is part of the 300Gbps network that is running on our redundant 400Gbps transport backbone to multiple Amsterdam and Frankfurt data centers. Route preferences are not specified, so you always get the shortest routes to other networks.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">It allows us to provide our clients with multiple ports, thus ensuring a complete redundancy.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b-container table, .b-container ol, .b-container ul {\r\nmargin-left: 250px;\r\n}\r\n.b-page__promo-title_black_yes {\r\ncolor: #fff;\r\n}\r\n</style>','section/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/96/_promo_news.jpg',NULL),(97,76,'/about/datacenter','datacenter',NULL,'Content_Page','Content_Section_Page','no','yes','yes','yes',40,'DataCenter',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicmedicondosc\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><strong>HOSTKEY&#39;S DATA CENTERS</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">HOSTKEY operates in state of art data centers in Russia (CITY SYSTEMS, DATALINE, DATAPRO) and the Netherlands (Serverius).</span></span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF692d;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklin