e=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://site-f.hostke.ru/upload/data_content/CitySystems-big.jpg\" style=\"width: 900px; height: 600px;\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nCity Systems data center was built in accordance with TIER II standards. It is located in a close proximity to Moscow city center. The data center is equipped with:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Two independent power supply systems.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Each system has the capacity of 1 MW.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">1250 kVA diesel generator set (DGS) operating in automatic mode.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Three uninterruptible power supply units (UPS) operating under N+1 scheme.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">300 kVA each, excess air conditioning and air humidifying systems.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><a id=\"dataline\" name=\"dataline\"></a>Automatic fire extinguishing systems.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Security systems for perimeter protection and unauthorized access prevention.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Including video surveillance system.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><b>DATALINE</b></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://site-f.hostke.ru/upload/data_content/DataLine-big.jpg\" style=\"width: 900px; height: 527px;\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nTIER III uncertified data center Dataline Nord was built in 2007 and is now offering its customers a possibility of placing equipment in a data center that has the following characteristics:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Total area of 10,684 square meters.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Total power capacity of 18200 KW.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Power per rack: 6 kW or higher.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">10 server rooms.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">1712 commercial racks.</span></span></span></li>\r\n